title: Ms. Marvel v2 01-50 + Specials (2006-2010)
description: This collection was in bits and pieces on here and was missing the Annual (along with a few dead torrents in-between), so I thought I'd repost it since it is such a great run and especially defines Carol Danvers for the modern era. This run was written by Brian Reed, and he takes Ms. Marvel all the way from just before Civil War all the way to Siege with numerous key storylines in-between. A great character study of a former Avenger trying to figure things out for herself, and smashing many things down in the process (figuratively and literally)! This torrent contains all 50 issues + the three specials which I have labeled as "b" numbering appropriate to where they belong. The specials are "Binary", "Storyteller" and the 2008 Annual. All credit and thanks to the original scanners and uploaders, please seed and enjoy! :-)
